Available in California, Colorado, Massachusetts, and Oklahoma currently.

attributes.name: Bloom Live Surf All-In-One 500mg | Pink Kush
Bloom Live Surf All-In-One 500mg | Gush Mintz
attributes.body:
Gush Mintz

Live Surf


Originating from the Bay Area, Gush Mintz is the epitome of a Cookies indica. Earthy, creamy, woodsy flavor notes precede a wave of relaxation. Fit for a sunny weekend in Sausalito.



Phenotype

Indica


Cross

Kush Mints x F1 Drub x Gushers


Notes

Almonds, Camphor, Pine Cones


Bloom Surf is the most advanced disposable vape on the market. Meticulously designed to preserve the rich terpene profiles in our oil, Bloom Surf is built with ceramic heating elements that prevent overheating and triple-airflow for bigger hits and better flavor.


Made with a 190mAh battery that provides more capacity than needed, the Surf ensures your battery will last long enough to finish every drop of oil.


Available in .5g for Bloom Classic, Bloom Live and Live Rosin.

attributes.name: Bloom Live Surf All-In-One 500mg | Grape Soda
attributes.body:
Enjoy the worry-free mellow mood of Grape Soda at home. This strain has a strong indica dominance, so it's perfect for a solo night in, like taking an online yoga class and watching a good movie. Or, enjoy a little Grape Soda in the tub and soak in a hot bath while immersing yourself in a good book.


Grape, pungent, sweet, citrus.


﻿Available in both vape and surf all-in-one.


Introducing the Surf All-In-One.

Technology: Proprietary triple intake airflow with ceramic heating.

Dose: 10-second maximum. Be careful.

Strains: Year-round Classic & seasonal Live.

Capacity: 500mg with 190mAh battery.

Use: Anywhere, anytime.

Warranty: Included.

Made to amplify terpenes.

Designed in Los Angeles, California.
